text: Janet Ruth Montgomery (born 29 October 1985) is an English movie and television actress. As of 2014, she stars in the TV series, Salem. She also had a role in the second season of Fox's Human Target. She played Eric Murphy's assistant Jennie in HBO's Entourage. == References == == Other websites == * Janet Montgomery on IMDb Category:1985 births Category:English actors Category:Living people
